luafilesystem: lua-filesystem (lua filesystem library)
luafilesystem:
luafilesystem: LuaFileSystem is a Lua library developed to complement the set
luafilesystem: of functions related to filesystems offered by the standard
luafilesystem: Lua distribution.
luafilesystem: LuaFileSystem offers a portable way to access the underlying
luafilesystem: directory structure and file attributes.
luafilesystem:
luafilesystem: homepage: http://keplerproject.github.com/luafilesystem/
